OL,6,FLord Mandelson's decision to resign
OL,7,Ffrom the Labour Party is the latest
OL,8,Ftwist in the fallout from his
OL,9,Fassociation with Jeffrey Epstein - a
OL,10,Frelationship that has already cost him
OL,11,Fhis job as UK ambassador to the United
OL,12,FStates and has now ended his long-
OL,13,Fstanding membership of a party he has
OL,14,Fspent much of his adult life serving.
