OL,6,FMandelson said he was stepping aside
OL,7,Fto spare Labour "further
OL,8,Fembarrassment" after fresh disclosures
OL,9,Femerged in the latest batch of Epstein-
OL,10,Frelated documents. Those revelations
OL,11,Fhave reignited questions not just
OL,12,Fabout his conduct, but also about
OL,13,Fdecision-making at the heart of
OL,14,Fgovernment.
OL,16,FFrom a political management point of
OL,17,Fview, the timing and handling of the
OL,18,Fsituation are now under the microscope.
