OL,3,CMandelson's resignation raises
OL,4,Cquestions over Labour's judgement
OL,6,FCritics, particularly from the
OL,7,Fopposition, argue that the government
OL,8,Fhas been regularly slow to respond to
OL,9,Fthis and that Mandelson's decision to
OL,10,Fresign, rather than being formally
OL,11,Fexpelled, shows weakness.
OL,13,FThat sense of a reactive, rather than
OL,14,Fproactive, response feeds into broader
OL,15,Fconcerns about judgment inside Number
OL,16,F10 - especially given that Mandelson
OL,17,Fhad already been removed from his
OL,18,Fambassadorial role last year following
OL,19,Fearlier revelations.
