OL,3,CMandelson's resignation raises
OL,4,Cquestions over Labour's judgement
OL,6,FMinisters I spoke to this morning
OL,7,Finsist that Sir Keir Starmer did not
OL,8,Fhave access to the full picture when
OL,9,FMandelson was appointed, and that once
OL,10,Fmore information came to light,
OL,11,Fdecisive action was taken.
OL,13,FThe Tories had previously called for
OL,14,Fall vetting material to be made
OL,15,Fpublic, while some Labour MPs are
OL,16,Fopenly criticising Starmer for
OL,17,Fappointing Mandelson in the first
OL,18,Fplace.
