OL,3,CMandelson's resignation raises
OL,4,Cquestions over Labour's judgement
OL,6,FThroughout his career, he has been no
OL,7,Fstranger to controversy, and some
OL,8,Fwithin the Labour Party had long
OL,9,Fquestioned whether it was ever wise to
OL,10,Fbring back someone with a well-
OL,11,Festablished reputation for attracting
OL,12,Fpolitical trouble. He has twice had to
OL,13,Fresign from cabinet, and there are
OL,14,Fquestions over whether it was wise to
OL,15,Fhave someone with a record like that
OL,16,Fin such a senior role again.
OL,18,FThe Conservatives are now pushing for
OL,19,Fa full inquiry and further
OL,20,Finvestigation.
